<p class="">Arising from the Prime Minister's reply with regard to this matter of the Opposition, is it not a fact that the small group led by the hon. Member for Bridgeton (Mr. Maxton) have, on the whole, been the best supporters of the Conservative party?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-08c08fa5-dca7-432c-ad88-08b66382fc71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
